In order to make things right,

00:17:50.920 --> 00:17:52.920
I prayed intensely to Jehovah.

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:57.039
I spent time in deep personal Bible study.

00:17:57.039 --> 00:17:58.720
My wife would also find articles

00:17:58.720 --> 00:18:00.839
about maintaining peace with the brothers

00:18:00.839 --> 00:18:02.880
and would give them to me to read.

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:04.720
She even selected kingdom songs

00:18:04.720 --> 00:18:06.440
that dealt with maintaining peace

00:18:06.440 --> 00:18:11.059
and she would sing them to me.

00:18:11.059 --> 00:18:13.259
I made a lot of changes to my attitude

00:18:13.259 --> 00:18:15.420
and worked hard to progress as a person

00:18:15.420 --> 00:18:16.859
whom Jehovah would approve.

00:18:18.019 --> 00:18:21.059
I tried to view my brothers the same way Jehovah did

00:18:21.059 --> 00:18:26.059
and to serve him with joy.

00:18:26.059 --> 00:18:28.539
I really wanted to give my best to Jehovah

00:18:28.539 --> 00:18:29.579
and to the brothers.

00:18:30.579 --> 00:18:33.700
At the same time, I did not want those wrong thoughts

00:18:33.700 --> 00:18:39.690
to ever come back into my heart.

00:18:39.690 --> 00:18:42.089
The valuable lessons that I have learned

00:18:42.089 --> 00:18:44.490
is that privileges are not more important.

00:18:44.490 --> 00:18:46.289
Rather, it is serving Jehovah

00:18:46.289 --> 00:18:48.289
that brings genuine happiness.

00:18:48.369 --> 00:18:51.609
And now I am finding real joy and satisfaction

00:18:51.609 --> 00:18:55.539
in my service to Jehovah.

00:18:55.539 --> 00:18:58.380
So may each of us prayerfully work

00:18:58.380 --> 00:19:03.380
to have the attitude of wanting to be a peacemaker.

00:19:03.940 --> 00:19:07.700
And when we do this, we prove to Jehovah

00:19:07.700 --> 00:19:11.380
we're the kinder person that he wants in his new world.

00:19:12.299 --> 00:19:15.980
In Psalm 37 11, it says of the new world,

00:19:15.980 --> 00:19:18.059
the make will possess the earth

00:19:18.059 --> 00:19:21.019
and they will find their exquisite delight

00:19:21.019 --> 00:19:23.900
in the abundance of peace.

00:19:23.900 --> 00:19:26.859
So the new world will be a very peaceful place.

00:19:26.859 --> 00:19:29.579
But if we're a peace promoter now,

00:19:29.579 --> 00:19:31.539
we will convince Jehovah

00:19:31.539 --> 00:19:35.819
that we will be an asset toward that peace of his new world.

00:19:35.819 --> 00:19:37.059
And think about this.

00:19:37.059 --> 00:19:40.500
In the new world, it will be natural

00:19:40.500 --> 00:19:44.619
for perfect people to just display peace.

00:19:44.619 --> 00:19:49.619
This beautiful aspect of the fruitage of Jehovah's Holy Spirit.

00:19:50.059 --> 00:19:52.339
But right now we have to work at it, don't we?

00:19:52.339 --> 00:19:54.220
We have to seek peace pursuant.

00:19:54.220 --> 00:19:57.660
But if we're a peace pursuer now,

00:19:57.660 --> 00:20:00.220
we will convince Jehovah

00:20:00.220 --> 00:20:03.460
that we will be a peace displayer

00:20:03.460 --> 00:20:05.259
in his righteous new world.

00:20:05.259 --> 00:20:07.460
And he'll want us to be there.

00:20:07.460 --> 00:20:10.099
So let's diligently promote peace

00:20:11.059 --> 00:20:14.180
and contribute toward the strength

00:20:14.180 --> 00:20:18.460
the happiness of Jehovah's beautiful organization,

00:20:18.460 --> 00:20:20.779
which really is a modern day miracle,

00:20:20.779 --> 00:20:25.619
remembering that those who promote peace have joy

00:20:25.619 --> 00:20:28.460
and they impart joy to others

00:20:28.460 --> 00:20:31.500
and they make Jehovah's heart rejoice.

00:20:31.500 --> 00:20:35.819
And all of that rejoicing will last forever.
